NAME

  Latin8 - Source code filter to escape Latin-8 script

SYNOPSIS

  use Latin8;

DESCRIPTION

  The Latin8 software provides character oriented Perl scripting
  environment in Latin-8 by easy installation and easy usage.

  - Character oriented regular expression
  - Byte oriented built-in functions
      and
  - Character oriented subroutines
  - Byte oriented regular expression on /b modifier

INSTALLATION

  Just copy Latin8.pm and Elatin8.pm to your @INC directory.
  for example, to C:\Perl\site\lib

SUBROUTINES

  Latin8::length(charstring)
  Latin8::substr(charstring, charpos, charlen)
  etc

SEE ALSO

  http://search.cpan.org/~ina/

